title: Avolon delivers one Boeing 737-800 aircraft to Aeromexico
text:
Avolon delivers one Boeing 737-800 aircraft to Aeromexico   
Aug 27, 2015 eTN   
DUBLIN, Ireland - Avolon, the international aircraft leasing company, today announces the delivery of a fourth Boeing 737-800 to Aeromexico. 
The delivery is the fourth of four Boeing 737-800 aircraft delivered to Aeromexico by Avolon.
